# graphify memory graph — scan root is ~/vault/memory/
# The memory graph ingests only DISTILLED notes (decisions/, notes/, INDEX.md).
# Everything below is raw/narrative/tooling and must stay out of the graph.
# (graphify-out/ and .graphify/ are auto-excluded by graphify; listed for clarity.)

**/chats/          # raw session transcripts written by /save-memory
**/doc/            # link-docs preview folders (repo-bound, not graph corpus)
templates/         # Obsidian note scaffolding
graphify/          # code-graphs rendered as browsable notes (redundant w/ repo graph)
graphify-out/      # the memory graph itself
.graphify/         # graphify's extraction cache
